name: Ai-search-engine
tagline: Lets make the soul for computers, lets bring machines to life !!
body:
### Introduction

Lets make the soul for computers, lets bring machines to life !!

This is a open source project. I am not a developer, but I wanted to initiate this project to build the largest Open Source Artificial intelligence (AI) Search Engine. 

I request everyone, all around the world, to start contributing to work together in this great project. I think it will be a great contribution to this world. Only together we will be able to create such an awesome software. 

Why wait for some money hungry corporate to create the best products, we can do it for ourselves. Lets make this the largest and most awesome project, and make it the next big revolution on how we interact with computers.
